    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Draugr Thrall is the lowest order of undead stirred in Svellheim's Fimbulwinter. Frost-blue skin stretches over brittle bone, tattered burial shrouds draped from skeletal frames. Hollow eyes glow faint green â€” not with intelligence, but with a dull, seething hunger for warmth.</p>",
